description: We are building a first of its kind smart marketing platform for creating, managing and tracking: - Affiliate - Referral - Network Marketing - Loyalty - Bounty programs and campaigns all from a single membership account powered by NEO smart contracts. Gagapay Network will also host an OPEN MARKETPLACE for businesses to publish campaign offers and individuals will be able to join any open campaign and market them to their existing network. By implementing targeted offers businesses will be able to reach the right marketers faster and grow a world wide network of customers. Let's be the connectors and build a platform for shared success!
name: Gagapay Network
